            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1ab0d903791f5643077a5680343b4ab1ed">
                <title>relatedByClassName ($matchClassNames)</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Return all the page models related to this tag (there may be multiple Page Classe attached so iterate through them all)</para>

<para>
                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters</title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>$matchClassNames</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>and array of classnames, a class name or a pattern as used by fnmatch, eg. &apos;*Page&apos; </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                <formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para></para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1a8d2cfef4c500a5a9fbfc9d4bc451c896">
                <title>getSourceFieldName ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Returns the name of the field on the model used to generate the tag, e.g. the &apos;<link linkend="d2/dde/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_title">Title</link>&apos; field.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1af9aa034ad033005279bd790155e683fa">
                <title>onBeforeWrite ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>If the <link linkend="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag">ModelTag</link> field is empty (length 0) then fill it with generated value. </para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1a0de7f13cc2c038bfdde8e2102c919a06">
                <title>HierarchicalModelTag ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Generate a full tag path walking up the chain via parents separated by config.hierarchical_source_separator. If the parent doesn&apos;t have <link linkend="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag">ModelTag</link> extension then self.fallbackFieldName will be used if supplied in extension ctor.</para>

<para>TODO test/debug this</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1abe54681d72f1b972bb437f7ec78b1ab6">
                <title>HierarchicalSource ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Generates a full tag path using the models &apos;Source&apos; field (e.g. &apos;<link linkend="d2/dde/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_title">Title</link>&apos;) instead of the tag field via the ParentID relationship specified in the extension ctor. Components will be separated by config.hierarchical_source_separator</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d5b/class_modular_1_1_fields_1_1_model_tag_1ad0ccc87f4ea1c9d55d0e0d92b61bf507">
                <title>ParentID ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>If a parent ID field name was specfied in extension ctor then return the ParentID value from the extended model.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>mixed </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
